The paper discusses the development of a type system for verifying mechanism design and differential privacy. This involves the study of algorithm design and probabilistic computations, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Game Theory (cs.GT), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
